<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2452?language=en' lang='en'>
This country isn't just carbon neutral — it's carbon negative
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Mar 2016
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
